      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be verified under a documented SQA plan with version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R1 was used under a documented SQA plan including version-controlled scripts, regression test suite, and audit trail. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
